criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Criteria for participation are women who:

               -  are over 17;

               -  can read Chinese;

               -  are at or over 24 weeks of gestation;

               -  pregnant with singleton;

               -  are not diagnosed of pregnancy complications such as preeclampsia, preterm labor,
                  preterm rupture of membranes, gestational diabetes, and cervical incompetence
                  before recruitment; and

               -  are willing to complete questionnaires and give blood samples.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  pregnant women who do not meet the recruitment criteria will be excluded from the
             study.
